(6.2-)7.3-8.3-9.4(-10.0) 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
, clavate, or subcylindrical, sometimes fusiform, apically mainly obtuse, occasionally mucronate, sometimes with 3-6 
