<normalizedToken originalValue="×">x</normalizedToken>
3.0-4.2-5.4(-6.8) 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μm">μm</normalizedToken>
, thin-walled, mainly clavate, occasionally fusiform, apically often obtuse or occasionally acute, occasionally with 2-4 
